            . I am a watchman on <placeName id="t18311201-246-crimeloc1312">Westminster-bridge</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18311201-246-crimeloc1312" type="placeName" value="Westminster-bridge"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18311201-246-crimeloc1312" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311201-246-off1310 t18311201-246-crimeloc1312"></join>. I met the prisoner on the Middlesex end of the bridge on the 20th of November, after nine o'clock at night; I saw him go and take this bundle out of a four-wheeled chaise, it was behind the driver - he had his right hand on the spring of the chaise as it passed me, and then I saw his left hand draw the bundle out; I took him - the chaise went on, but I advertized the property, and found the owner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18311201-246-person1879">
